{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "臨界值", "storyInfo": "身為深池頭領的蔓德拉正準備前去聚會，得到了聚會地點被洩露的消息。風笛和號角混入聚會，正與詩人交流，卻遭到上校帶兵包圍。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊貴的女士，很榮幸通知您，晚宴已經準備好了——", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真慢。你們這些貴族，做什麼事都拖拖拉拉的，煩死了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我招待不周，請容許我向您致以最真誠的歉意。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是省省吧。今天到底能來幾個人？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個小丘郡的有識之士都收到了邀請，包括我們最近廣受歡迎的大詩人，西莫·威廉姆斯......", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩人？聽起來就沒勁。你答應要找的貴族和商人呢？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然......當然，他們也會來。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如南部地區紡織品產業的領頭人波萊爵士，獲得過麥考伊獎的巴希爾醫生，還有擁有十數家鋼鐵廠的埃文斯先生......", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？你說的這些人，尤其是最後那個，他們都確定會來？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，他們中的一部分已經到了。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽聞有最尊貴的客人到場，還有好幾位名流雅士從其他城市趕來，就是為了能一睹您和您的同伴們的風采。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我按照您的要求，製作了這份名單，您隨時都可以看看——", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話多了點，活幹得倒是還行。好了，你可以下去了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您慷慨的褒獎。等您準備好了還請通知我，我迫不及待地想看我那不起眼的小廳因您的到來熠熠生輝。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還站著幹嘛？話不都說完了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，請允許我問最後一個問題——那位最尊貴的女士，她有沒有哪怕一絲可能性也會蒞臨現場？", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這不是你能問的問題。快滾吧。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_228_1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓德拉，你怎麼看起來心煩意亂的？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少來這套，假惺惺的，聽得我噁心。誰都知道你阿赫茉妮不會真的關心人。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，那我只好換個說法——你這樣愚蠢地踱來踱去，擋到我的光了。我還想把這本可愛的小說看完呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們有錢人是不是都這副樣子？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放這麼多樂器，買幾本書，彷彿把門面裝點得滿滿當當以後，別人就不會注意到那實際上空空蕩蕩的腦子。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有門面能裝點，總比由內到外都空無一物要好吧？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#4"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，好吧。看來你一時半會不願意消停了。要不然這樣，如果你在為不知道舞會中先邁哪條腿而發愁，我會領著你跳。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在胡說什麼啊！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是在想大事。這次來這麼多貴族和富商，要是我們能得到他們的支持，到時候何止佔領區區一個小丘郡，就連拿下倫蒂尼姆都——", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓德拉，你該停下了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都什麼時候了，你就不能放下你那本破書？你心裡到底有沒有在為領袖和我們的大事考慮？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是在說你這慌亂無措的腳步。我是說，你該停下你的這些胡言亂語和你的小腦袋裡在琢磨的荒唐事了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你叫我現在停下？怎麼可能！為了這次計畫，從部署安插人手，到忍著噁心安排這次集會，我一路上付出了多少心血？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就等不及了，我等不及看深池的火燒穿這座城市，撕裂我們腳下這虛假的龐然大物！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你呢？你和那個恬不知恥地佔了本該屬於領袖的榮光的假貨——", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的，真的，該閉嘴了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼時候——輪到你替領袖做決定了？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖——", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，是我。是的，我們還在這裡。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總算變得有意思了一點點。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我們不用在這裡爭辯你那些冒冒失失的小計畫是否可行了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那傢伙傳來的消息？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人查到了這個地方。今天晚上的集會，來的恐怕不止是你請來的那些小朋友。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......軍隊裡的人？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多。哎呀，說不定還有我的熟人呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，我真想——", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收起你的法杖吧，會有機會的。不過，不是現在。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該走了，我們還有別的事要做。這裡交給她，說不定馬上就會有一場好戲。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵......我開始幻想這間討人厭的屋子碎裂成渣的樣子了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，沒想到我們混進來這麼容易。我還以為......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要想辦法潛入？那也不是不行。只不過，走正門的話，找人說話會更方便。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我的駐軍朋友拿來的消息很寶貴，知道這場聚會的人並不多啊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有很多隱秘的貴族聚會都以這種方式舉行——他們往往認為邀請函太俗套。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要有獲知資訊的管道，加上證明身份的信物，就擁有了跨過這道門檻的資格。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，你都沒跟我說過你家是那麼有名氣的貴族。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有區別嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在學校裡的時候，貴族同學總是自成一派，學習上當然還是在一起，可下課以後他們都不怎麼和我們一起活動的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你喜歡那套繁文縟節？只能穿一次的禮服，每周都在變的流行妝容，翻來覆去的寒暄。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，你還是別說了，我其實陪好朋友去過那麼一兩次這種場合，光是回憶一下吃飯時候該先用哪種叉子，我的腦袋就想當場炸開。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛好，我也沒那麼喜歡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是再不情願也不得不承認，這個與生俱來的姓氏偶爾還是會帶來一些便利。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，今天來這裡集會的人，他們都是鬼魂部隊的支持者嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我看未必。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威廉姆斯先生，終於見到您了！聽說您也會來，我特地從半島郡趕了過來，就為了請您在我這本珍藏的詩集上簽個名。", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，美麗的女士，這是我的榮幸。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西莫，我最親愛的大詩人！你在這裡。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛讀完你新出版的歷史小故事。多麼有趣的文章啊，我第一次知道，原來我們塔拉人還有這麼多雄奇瑰麗的過去。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，不過是幾篇基於民間傳說改編的幻想之作。我工作的最大價值只是將被風沙掩埋的瑰寶挖掘出一角，好讓更多人看見。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您真是太謙虛了。您筆下的那位一手締造了最輝煌的塔拉文明的德拉克蓋爾王，是多麼英明偉岸，足以走進我每一個心潮澎湃的夢境——", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是如此。在我眼裡，你就和萊塔尼亞最偉大的音樂家一樣，有機會改變一個時代！", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......您的話太誇張了。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你願意，整個維多利亞的出版商大門都願意為你敞開，大家都等著把你的作品翻譯成不同的文字。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時候，這片大地上的每個國家都將意識到，我們塔拉文化有自己的獨特魅力，不該被埋沒在維多利亞一成不變的機器轟鳴聲中。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是真能這樣就好了。如果有越來越多的國際人士支持我們，我們的聲音就越容易讓公爵們和議會聽見。", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說的是啊！一樣是維多利亞公民，只因為我的某個曾曾曾祖父是蓋爾王的臣子，我就要交更多的遺產稅，多麼荒唐！", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便如此，埃文斯先生，您還是慷慨地雇傭了足夠多的同胞，為大家提供了在這座優雅的城市立足的機會。", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您和您的家族不愧是我們塔拉人的驕傲。", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈，是啊，我們的同胞，他們想找到一份體面的工作可不容易，我聽說他們在廠裡辛苦勞作一周，只能得到這麼點鑄幣。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......而其他出身的維多利亞工人，能在你的廠裡賺到兩倍。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳......", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "容我不合時宜地說一句——想讓強鄰們認可我們，可沒那麼容易吧？", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位請想一想，光靠音樂和詩歌，萊塔尼亞如何能成為今日的萊塔尼亞？", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如萊塔尼亞有令人生畏的術師——", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們塔拉人若想得到更多國家的認可，還是要依靠更加實際的力量，比如一些來自遠方朋友的......技術支援。", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我恰好有那麼一點獲得贊助的管道，我很樂意借這機會與男爵閣下的朋友們分享。", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，您說的一點都沒錯！任何資助都很重要，若是兩手空空，再靈巧的舌頭也有因乾渴而無力表達的那一天。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此看來，我與在座諸位都一樣，我們都在渴望著一個全新的時代——那麼，我們為何不為這共同的夢想舉杯呢？", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是一個令人振奮的夜晚......奇怪，威廉姆斯先生到哪裡去了？", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上好，威廉姆斯先生。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，女士。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我沒有打擾您。您是在創作嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，只是一首小詩，已經好幾天了，我還沒有完成。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本以為這次聚會能帶給我一些靈感，現在看來，寫作的事還是沒法強求。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "類似場合總是會過快地消耗人的精力。您是不是也覺得有些疲憊？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......被發現了。要不是查理斯——我是說男爵大人的邀請實在太過熱情，我還是更偏好在自家壁爐旁的閱讀之夜。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰又不是呢？我打賭每個願意參加這類活動的人，都是迫於生計。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡這個說法。女士，你不是塔拉人吧？", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您猜的沒錯，我想這一帶的居民裡魯珀並不多見。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我無意以種族來判斷出身。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然你有意在選擇更符合我們習慣的詞彙，但是你的口音還是暴露了自己——這是受過倫蒂尼姆標準教育的維多利亞貴族才有的口音。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是大詩人，非常敏銳。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "創作的第一步是觀察。我甚至能看出來，你和他們的來意也有所不同。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在懷疑我？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#4"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懷疑什麼呢？我來這裡，只是為了交流一些思想，而你正在與我交流。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕我不是塔拉人？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因為你不是塔拉人。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一杯麥芽酒，謝謝——你想喝什麼嗎，女士？", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不用了，能站在窗口吹吹風就挺好。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那繼續我們愉快的聊天吧。剛才說到哪了？", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦對，語言和文字正是為了交流而生，既包括過去和未來的對話，也包括此時此地我與你之間的閒談。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是您在體諒我。要是您使用塔拉語，我可就與耳聾無異了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，在這場宴會裡，你很難聽到塔拉語。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才想起來，我讀過的您的作品也都是用維多利亞語寫成的。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "韻腳會限制詩人的想像力。維多利亞的詩歌讀起來與萊塔尼亞的風味就很不一樣。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很喜歡讀古塔拉語寫就的詩歌，讀著這些文字就彷彿觸摸歷史的另一面。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我並不打算偽裝自己。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小說著維多利亞語長大，我的思想已被語言塑造，如果我換成塔拉語來寫作，就成了穿著大小不合適的鞋跳舞的小丑。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說有很多人在渴望著塔拉文化的復興——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我也是其中一員。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的城市在大地上流浪，這片土地既是不變的，又時時刻刻都在發生變化。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許有一天塔拉語會重新成為構築我們孩子們的頭腦的語言，而我樂於擁抱這種改變。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果——有人希望這種變化能夠迅速地、甚至逆轉自然趨勢地爆發呢？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“思想有什麼用？你在土裡種下一根羽毛，想像它長成一隻羽獸。”", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......出自您出版的第一本詩集，是我特別喜歡的句子。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我對這個問題的回答。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我自己眼中，我不能，也並不想改變這片土地，我只是那個努力種下羽毛的人。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而思想本該是自由的，無人能夠干涉——在每個人心裡長出來的羽獸可能各不相同，就如大家對這片土地的未來都有著不同的期望。", "name": "詩人威廉姆斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了，威廉姆斯先生。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "容我發自內心地說一句，與您聊天真的很愉快。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#6"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，不太對勁。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大提琴他們有超過四十分鐘沒有發來任何消息了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們本來不該在軍營應付駐軍嗎？你要求他們每半個小時都要發一次信。我們剛剛動身的時候，大提琴還跟我抱怨這任務太無聊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......你覺不覺得周圍有點太安靜了？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在窗口守著，本來能看見廣場上人來人往。可是突然之間，好像發生了什麼事，人們都跑開了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，之前跟蹤我們的是駐軍的人......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宴會廳的大門忽然被踹開。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數十名全副武裝的士兵闖了進來。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paniccrowd", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊，怎麼回事？為什麼突然會冒出來這麼多士兵？", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "竟然膽敢用武器指著我......你們瞭解我們的身份嗎？", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰，誰把秘密傳出去的？！", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死......得快點離開這裡！", "name": "貪婪的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（快，快去通知蔓德拉女士，就說我們有麻煩了......）", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（什麼？！你說他們全都走了？什麼時候的事？一個小時之前？！）", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（你這個廢物......！）", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全都不許動！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士們先生們，是的，沒錯，你們——統統被捕了。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}